reviewText: Excellent!  Cannot get enough of Jonathan Cahn.  God seems to reveal deep things to him.  Takes me deeper into the true meaning of Scripture since I am not Jewish.  We seem to miss so much not understanding the culture and mind set of the Jewish people.  He clarify's it all.
This is one of the best buys that I every did- Both my husband and I have learned so much from volume 1 and volume 2. I highly recommend this to anyone who wants to learn.
Intense!  Almost information overload but, awesome information. You will be watching it several times to get it all.
loved the DVDs.  Rabbi Cahn's teachings inspire me.

Best set of teachings I have ever heard in my life.  Bringing Old and New Testimate together as it should be and is!!!  You must understand if Jesus is your Lord and Savior...he is Jewish and is the Jewish Messiah.  Thank you Jonathan, Check out his other teachings on youtube....super awesome.
